{
  "text": "To facilitate our research findings being available to the widest possible audience (e.g. patients with MS and healthcare providers), [CITATION_1] our wider research team agreed to the dissemination of results in an open access healthcare journal. In our presentation, we focused on thematic differences in our six heterogeneous groups, and during our analysis, we were particularly interested in the experiences of sufficiently active groups (i.e. Groups 3 and 6) in comparison with experiences of those who were less active (i.e. Groups 1, 2, 4 and 5). We made comparison between groups and within the entire sample.",
